{"tid":2196732,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"WhatsApp傾股票》警方傳拘至少十人涉操縱壹傳媒股價","createTime":"2020-09-10T06:14:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-10T08:49:47.000Z","uid":13663,"like":21,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"29faee0f826600f9b7773cdb0628dc8127d36f1b","tid":2196732,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T06:14:58.000Z","msg":"報道指，有關人士涉及上月在壹傳媒創辦人黎智英及多名高層被捕後，操控股價。據該報了解，拘捕行動是近日進行，其中一名人涉操縱股價中賺利2,000萬元，另一人賺70萬元。報道指，警方將於下午向傳媒交待事件。<br />\n<br />\n另有媒體引述消息指，毒品調查科拘捕15人涉嫌利用WhatsApp作溝通工具，透過買賣壹傳媒股票，舞高弄低股價，高位獲利，其中一名被捕人更從中獲利超過2500萬港元，警方會在今日下午4時在警察總部交代案件詳情。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a551d4988c781268ac803397393882301ee0c07f","tid":2196732,"uid":13663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T06:15:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200910/GLR526QO5FEMZF7UQERJKVFZ7A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200910%2FGLR526QO5FEMZF7UQERJKVFZ7A%2F&d=8aZ3B%2FsgtJclBbEiVdGGEwKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=6c498fc7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200910%2FGLR526QO5FEMZF7UQERJKVFZ7A%2F&h=02c46a8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200910/GLR526QO5FEMZF7UQERJKVFZ7A/</a>"},{"pid":"6a660154dda4a2cb0f876367b5d3f459a8cf7574","tid":2196732,"uid":152476,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T06:15:31.000Z","msg":"毒品調查科？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbec7ad7e09fedd6c31172f5de1499a91da726d5","tid":2196732,"uid":810,"like":18,"dislike":3,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T06:15:56.000Z","msg":"快撚啲開記召柒出國際<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f181a60e111cb933707dd